Am I the only one who finds containers and the put verb to be cumbersome.  Wish they worked like use and give.  It would also be a lot easier to cover all the&quot; put object1 in object2&quot; variations the user might come up with if the equivalent of giveanything and givetoanything where available for put.  Anyways, I've now learned to limit my use of containers.

